Pulling the changes:
	git pull

Creating a new branch(lakitas):
	git branch lakitas

Switching to lakitas branch:
	git checkout lakitas

Creating Changelog:
	touch Changelog_lakitas

Adding the changes and changelog to local lakitas:
	git add -A

Commiting the added changes to local lakitas:
	git commit -m 'Tidying up the strings sent to sentence()'

Pushing the local repository:
	git push origin lakitas

Merge changes to master:
	git checkout master
	git merge lakitas

Pushing the changes:
	git push

Correcting the undeleted merged junk

Finishing the Changelog file

Repeating last 5 steps:
	git checkout lakitas
	git push origin lakitas
	git checkout master
	git merge lakitas
	git push